OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChilly start, then bright
OL,6,Fspells through the morning but cloud
OL,7,Fthickens through the afternoon,
OL,8,Fperhaps bringing some patchy light
OL,9,Frain eastwards later. Winds light but
OL,10,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with some reasonable
OL,13,Fbreaks to start becoming overcast with
OL,14,Frain by the morning. The wind increase
OL,15,Fovernight becoming breezy at times and
OL,16,Fblustery along the coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FRain and strong winds
OL,19,FSaturday morning, clearing to sunny
OL,20,Fspells and isolated showers.
OL,21,FTemperatures mostly around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
