OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday,
OL,6,Fbreezy with sunshine and showers.
OL,7,FMonday, scattered showers but lighter
OL,8,Fwinds. Tuesday turns more settled with
OL,9,Fsome isolated showers. Temperatures
OL,10,Fmostly around average.
